   "source": [
    "print(pol_aparts.info())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Choose top-10 cities per amount of advertisments to get cleat graph\n",
    "top_cities = pol_aparts['city'].value_counts().nlargest(10).index\n",
    "df_top = pol_aparts[pol_aparts['city'].isin(top_cities)]\n",
    "\n",
    "# List of categorical columns for analisys\n",
    "cat_features = ['type', 'buildingMaterial', 'condition', 'hasElevator', \n",
    "                'hasParkingSpace', 'ownership', 'hasBalcony', 'hasSecurity', 'hasStorageRoom']\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create loop\n",
    "for feature in cat_features:\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(17, 9))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Build graph\n",
    "    sns.boxplot(\n",
    "        data=df_top, \n",
    "        x='city', \n",
    "        y='price_per_m2', \n",
    "        hue=feature,\n",
    "        order=top_cities, # Set order of cities with ascending\n",
    "        palette='Set2'\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Set style\n",
    "    plt.title(f'Influence \"{feature}\" on price per square meter in top-10 cities', fontsize=15)\n",
    "    plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('Price per square meter (PLN)')\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('City')\n",
    "    plt.grid(axis='y', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7) # Сетка для удобства сравнения цен\n",
    "    plt.legend(title=feature, bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc='upper left') # Выносим легенду\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c38c7558-2f81-443d-8345-4b1312caab12",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Insights features \"Type\"\n",
    "- Type \"Apartment buildong\" is highly rated in all cities.\n",
    "- Type \"Block of flats\" is reted higher than type \"Tenement\" in cities: Wroclaw, Lodz, Bydgoszcz, Poznan, Szczecin, Katowice.\n",
    "- Type \"Tenement\" is reted higher than type \"Block of flats\" in cities:  Warszawa, Krakow, Gdynia\n",
    "- Type 'Apartment building' rated twice highter than other types in Gdansk. Tenement equal block of flats.\n",
    "### Insights features \"building Material\"\n",
    "- Brick apartments rated highter in all cities except Szczecin. Diffrents in building material haven't in Bydgoszcz\n",
    "### Insights features \"Condition\"\n",
